rugs) <VZambudio@londondrugs.com>,Design\n124: ,,,1,Navigate to https://www.londondrugs.com/cart,Cart page loads,,,\n125: ,,,2,Wait for cart summary/subtotal to load,Cart subtotal is visible = True,,,\n126: 83243,Test Case,My Account — Signing in with valid email and password redirects user to My Account dashboard,,,,My Account,LD.com - Globant,Virginia Zambudio (On Behalf of London Drugs) <VZambudio@londondrugs.com>,Design\n127: ,,,1,Navigate to https://www.londondrugs.com/myaccount/login,Login page loads,,,\n128: ,,,2,Wait for email input field to be visible,Verify step completes successfully,,,\n129: ,,,3,Enter registered email address (USER_EMAIL env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n130: ,,,4,Enter password (USER_PASSWORD env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n131: ,,,5,Click 'Sign In' button,Verify step completes successfully,,,\n132: ,,,6,Wait for My Account redirect,Redirected to My Account after login = /myaccount,,,\n133: 83244,Test Case,\"My Account — Filling address form with name, street, city and postal code saves new address in address book list\",,,,My Account,LD.com - Globant,Virginia Zambudio (On Behalf of London Drugs) <VZambudio@londondrugs.com>,Design\n134: ,,,1,Navigate to https://www.londondrugs.com/myaccount/address-book (with auth session),Address book page loads,,,\n135: ,,,2,Click 'Add New Address' button,Verify step completes successfully,,,\n136: ,,,3,Fill first name (TEST_FIRSTNAME env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n137: ,,,4,Fill last name (TEST_LASTNAME env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n138: ,,,5,Fill street address (TEST_ADDRESS env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n139: ,,,6,Fill city (TEST_CITY env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n140: ,,,7,Fill postal code (TEST_POSTAL env variable),Verify step completes successfully,,,\n141: ,,,8,Click 'Save' to submit address form,Verify step completes successfully,,,\n142: ,,,9,Wait for new address 