[12:53:07] {"event": "tool_call", "tool": "think", "args": {"thought": "\nNow I have the full CSV. Let me organize the test cases by epic/area:\n\n**Epics (by Area Path):**\n- EPIC-01: Home Page → TC IDs: 83225, 83226, 83227, 83228, 83229, 83230, 83231, 83232\n- EPIC-02: PLP → TC IDs: 83233, 83234, 83248\n- EPIC-03: PDP → TC IDs: 83235, 83236, 83237, 83238, 83239, 83240, 83247\n- EPIC-04: Cart → TC IDs: 83241, 83242\n- EPIC-05: My Account → TC IDs: 83243, 83244\n- EPIC-06: Store Locator → TC IDs: 83245, 83246\n- EPIC-07: MyRegistry → TC ID: 83247\n- EPIC-08: Checkout → TC IDs: 83249, 83250\n\nNote: 83247 (MyRegistry) is under PDP area but has MyRegistry area path. 83248 (Deals and Events) is under PLP area path.\n\nLet me re-check area paths:\n- 83225-83232: Home Page\n- 83233-83234: PLP \n- 83235-83240: PDP\n- 83241-83242: Cart\n- 83243-83244: My Account\n- 83245-83246: Store Locator\n- 83247: MyRegistry\n- 83248: PLP (Deals and Events)\n- 83249-83250: Checkout\n\nSESSION_ID = qed-001\nFTC_FOLDER = /Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/artifacts/outputs/quality-engineering-design/test-cases/\nSUITES_SUBFOLDER = .../test-cases/suites/\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Read reference files (phase-a-epic-func-suites.md, func-test-cases-template.md)\n2. Generate Gherkin suites per epic - INLINE sequential (delegation UNAVAILABLE)\n3. Write files immediately (Write-Flush-Forget)\n\nEPICS scoped:\n- EPIC-01: Home Page (8 TCs)\n- EPIC-02: PLP / Search (3 TCs)  \n- EPIC-03: PDP (7 TCs)\n- EPIC-04: Cart (2 TCs)\n- EPIC-05: My Account (2 TCs)\n- EPIC-06: Store Locator (2 TCs)\n- EPIC-07: MyRegistry (1 TC - BLOCKED)\n- EPIC-08: Checkout (2 TCs)\n\nLet me read the reference files briefly then start generating.\n"}}
